title: Chinonso Emeka
text:
Chinonso Emeka (born 30 August 2001) is a Nigerian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for Belgian club <a href="K.A.A.%20Gent">Gent</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Belgian%20First%20Division%20A">Belgian First Division A</a> debut for <a href="K.A.A.%20Gent">Gent</a> on 22 May 2021 in a game against <a href="KV%20Mechelen">Mechelen</a>.
International career.
He was included in the Nigeria's squad for the <a href="2019%20FIFA%20U-20%20World%20Cup">2019 FIFA U-20 World Cup</a>, but did not appear in any games.
